  <brief_title>A Trial In Patients With Advanced Cancer And Leukemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I Trial Of Pf-03084014 In Patients With Advanced Solid Tumor Malignancy And T-cell Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia/Lymphoblastic Lymphoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
